title: Mojo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Salad bar, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A cafe-style place, with counter service that serves breakfast and lunch. It has a healthy orientation and claims to also follow the 'dirty dozen', sourcing organic and local where possible. The food is mostly vegan, and most of it is gluten-free, nut free, etc. Everything is labelled. Also have a range of pre-made and made-to-order smoothies, juices and healthy desserts. Service is quick and although the place is small, there is usually place to sit. Offers a meal deal.
